ENTRY       EC 4.2.3.131                Enzyme
NAME        miltiradiene synthase;
            SmMDS;
            SmiKSL
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-oxygen lyases;
            Acting on phosphates
SYSNAME     (+)-copaly-diphosphate diphosphate-lyase (cyclizing, miltiradiene-forming)
REACTION    (+)-copalyl diphosphate = miltiradiene + diphosphate [RN:R10585]
ALL_REAC    R10585
SUBSTRATE   (+)-copalyl diphosphate [CPD:C11901]
PRODUCT     miltiradiene [CPD:C20711];
            diphosphate [CPD:C00013]
COMMENT     Isolated from the plant Selaginella moellendorffii as a mutifunctional enzyme that also catalyses EC 5.5.1.12, copalyl diphosphate synthase [2]. In the plant Salvia miltiorrhiza the two enzymes are separate entities [1].
